Package: cloud-iot
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-pip, python3-venv, nginx, curl, openssl
Maintainer: Lika Digital <info@lika.digital>
Description: Cloud IoT Marina Pedestal Management System
 Full-stack IoT dashboard for marina smart pedestal management.
 Includes FastAPI backend, React frontend, ML-based berth detection,
 MQTT integration, customer portal, billing, and chat.
 .
 Components:
  - FastAPI backend (Python 3.11+, SQLite, JWT auth, WebSocket)
  - React 18 frontend served via nginx
  - MQTT broker (Eclipse Mosquitto, Docker)
  - ML worker with RT-DETR + DINOv2 berth detection (Docker)
